snippet.textDisplay:
Would it be possible to build a terrarium with tubbings around the outside, so that you could possibly still see the queen later in their empire?


Edit: Just wanted to add on that I've been subscribed to this channel for a while, and it's always really nice to reconnect to the fascination I had with ants as a child. I really wanted to have an ant farm and be able to observe them, but I was too young and not responsible enough, haha. But here's to hoping that someday soon, I will have the money and the space to create my own little kingdom to be the best it can be.


I've even debated caring for and breeding my own crickets to give to my colony, but I'm unsure. I have a hard time killing bugs unless they're wounded already.
